Grondement de tonnerre

730
01:23:49,541 --> 01:24:02,416
...

731
01:24:11,666 --> 01:24:12,875
-C'est...

732
01:24:13,750 --> 01:24:15,125
C'est ton fils.

733
01:24:15,291 --> 01:24:17,083
